<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">        &quot;- **skill-creator**: Generate new skill definitions</span><span style="--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;">\\n\\n</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">&quot;</span></span>
