<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">        &quot;1. Load the relevant skill(s) to get detailed instructions</span><span style="--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;">\\n</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">&quot;</span></span>
